COMMENT ON COLUMN event_morse_supplier_claimed.morse_node_address IS 'The hex-encoded address of the Morse non-custodial (i.e. operator) account. - Unstaked balance was migrated 1:1 - Stake was migrated 1:1 from morse_node_address to shannon_operator_address - Morse non-custodial (i.e. operator) address. If morse_output_address was not set, this is the custodial address. - See ''pocket nodes --help'' for more information. Note that this refers to the Morse CLI. E.g.: 00f9900606fa3d5c9179fc0c8513078a53a2073e';
COMMENT ON COLUMN event_morse_supplier_claimed.morse_output_address IS 'ONLY applicable to Morse node/supplier accounts. Hex-encoded address of the Morse output account/wallet associated with the Morse node/supplier. - E.g.: 00f9900606fa3d5c9179fc0c8513078a53a2073e - Morse custodial (i.e. owner) address, which owned the staked tokens of the operator. See ''pocket nodes --help'' for more information. Note that this refers to the Morse CLI.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN event_morse_supplier_claimed.claim_signer_type IS 'The type of supplier claim signer, indicating which actor executed the claim and whether it was a custodial or non-custodial claim. - MORSE_SUPPLIER_CLAIM_SIGNER_TYPE_NON_CUSTODIAL_SIGNED_BY_ADDR - MORSE_SUPPLIER_CLAIM_SIGNER_TYPE_CUSTODIAL_SIGNED_BY_OPERATOR - MORSE_SUPPLIER_CLAIM_SIGNER_TYPE_CUSTODIAL_SIGNED_BY_OWNER';
-- COMMENT refreshes (proto docstring changed since previous version)
COMMENT ON COLUMN event_morse_supplier_claimed.session_end_height IS 'Shannon session end height in which the claim was committed';
COMMENT ON COLUMN event_morse_supplier_claimed.claimed_balance_amount IS 'Unstaked balance claimed from Morse';
COMMENT ON COLUMN event_morse_supplier_claimed.claimed_balance_denom IS 'Unstaked balance claimed from Morse';
COMMENT ON COLUMN event_morse_supplier_claimed.claimed_supplier_stake_amount IS 'Supplier stake claimed as a result of the claim - Equivalent to Morse supplier staked amount';
COMMENT ON COLUMN event_morse_supplier_claimed.claimed_supplier_stake_denom IS 'Supplier stake claimed as a result of the claim - Equivalent to Morse supplier staked amount';
COMMENT ON COLUMN event_morse_supplier_claimed.supplier IS 'Supplier staked as a result of the claim - Mirrors Morse supplier stake';
